3. cs.CG (Computational Geometry): The problem of fitting curves to unorganized data points is a common problem in computational geometry. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper proposes a numerical optimization method for fitting B-spline curves, which falls under the scope of numerical analysis.
